e clear that further progress would require additional funding and staff resources. Consideration needs to be given to strengthening the resources </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">given to institutions such as</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> the Scottish Resource C</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">entre for Women in STEM,</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> the UK Equality Challenge Unit</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">and other</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> similar organisations </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">to support academic institutions seeking to achieve </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">progress in the Athena Swan Awards programme.</span></li></ol><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 36pt; text-align:justify"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><ol start="5" type="1" style="margin:0pt; padding-left:0pt"><li style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt; margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 31.25pt; padding-left:4.75pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">T</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">he Scottish Government </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">has </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">written a</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">very supportive letter to the </span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt">RSE on the</span><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:11pt"> recommendations of the Report</span><a name="_ftnre